WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.308
Hey, good morning family! I'm excited to be with you all today.

00:00:04.309 --> 00:00:10.480
This video has been a challenge to get up; I've gone through some stuff to get this one up today.

00:00:10.481 --> 00:00:14.323
It's been pretty rough; five times I've been interrupted, but I'm determined.

00:00:14.324 --> 00:00:23.523
I'm going to get this video done because I know what the Lord has for you today, and I know that this is going to help you.

00:00:23.524 --> 00:00:29.807
Anytime the enemy tries to come in and show himself off like this, it is for a purpose.

00:00:29.808 --> 00:00:44.479
He is threatened by what I'm about to tell you today, so please stay tuned and listen to this. I'm telling you, he is being a rascal. Here we go.

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:53.942
When I was praying during Rosh Hashanah yesterday, there were a lot of things the Lord showed me in the spirit realm.

00:00:53.943 --> 00:01:00.874
Whenever I was in my secret place praying, he told me some stuff I can't talk about.

00:01:00.875 --> 00:01:07.474
I'm going to tell you what I can tell you, and then we're going to go from there.

00:01:07.475 --> 00:01:20.016
I'm going to talk about authority, but part of the word that he gave me about Rosh Hashanah, he said, 'My calendar is from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.'It's the Jewish calendar.

00:01:20.017 --> 00:01:45.910
He said yours, of course, is January 1st to January 1st, but he said from this September until the next Rosh Hashanah—which sometimes is in October, it's a fall feast—he said you are going to see a lot of suppression coming from the internet, from Facebook, and from all of the major social media sites, from YouTube.

00:01:45.911 --> 00:01:56.923
All this suppression of freedom of speech, freedom of basically what you think. You're on their platform, so they are going to...

00:01:56.924 --> 00:02:09.455
I saw them in meetings, I saw things happening, and they are going to start attacking a lot of free speech, freedom of speech, being able to talk about the elections, and about religious stuff.

00:02:09.456 --> 00:02:18.283
The thing for your arm, you know, they're going to talk about that; they're going to suppress that.

00:02:18.284 --> 00:02:23.322
There's a lot of things the Lord showed me, that there's going to be a lot of suppression.

00:02:23.323 --> 00:02:29.135
He was telling me about this and that it was going to increase a lot.

00:02:29.136 --> 00:02:38.528
He said from Rosh Hashanah again, this will be a time of great acceleration of change.

00:02:38.529 --> 00:02:49.878
He said you will see change accelerate like on warp speed. Even more so, he referred to it as birthing pains.

00:02:49.879 --> 00:03:02.614
He was showing me that just like a woman goes into labor, the birthing pains are slow at the beginning and then they pick up.

00:03:02.615 --> 00:03:13.518
The closer you get to the baby being born, the birthing pains increase. Every woman who has had a child would know that.

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:21.071
What the Lord showed me was that they will increase during Rosh Hashanah every time it's a Jewish New Year.

00:03:21.072 --> 00:03:31.038
Until his coming, we will see those birthing pains increase clear up to that year, and you're going to see it be significant.

00:03:31.039 --> 00:03:42.494
That is a time frame to always watch. I try to talk to you all about the Shemitah cycles and how it's every seven years.

00:03:42.495 --> 00:03:52.829
That's why people were asking me, 'When do you believe the Rapture is going to take place?'I believe the Rapture of the church will take place at the end of a Shemitah cycle.

00:03:52.830 --> 00:04:05.833
If the calendar and everything is right, we just had a cycle last year, so we would have six more years until the next Shemitah cycle starts.

00:04:05.834 --> 00:04:13.988
That's a great time for the Rapture of the church, in my opinion.

00:04:13.989 --> 00:04:20.523
People have asked me about the Revelation 12 sign and all that. I believe we're going to see that.

00:04:20.524 --> 00:04:30.079
They've wondered about September 23rd and if that is a significant day. I know the world acknowledges it.

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:36.845
There are people saying there are all kinds of movies and all this stuff about it, but I believe the Revelation 12 sign...

00:04:36.846 --> 00:04:51.831
I'm not real big on all the Bible verses, but Robert Breaker is brilliant, and so is Pastor Steve with Discover Ministries.

00:04:51.832 --> 00:05:02.706
He's brilliant with the Bible. I would encourage anybody to go and join his online church at Discover Ministries and find him on YouTube.

00:05:02.707 --> 00:05:14.261
Pastor Steve is brilliant with the Word, far more than all the scriptures he knows and how he is able to make the Bible come alive.

00:05:14.262 --> 00:05:23.996
I'd encourage anybody to go over there, join his church online, and listen to that. He has so much amazing information for you to learn.

00:05:23.997 --> 00:05:32.370
I didn't even know it was all over there at his Discover Church; he has an amazing app.

00:05:32.371 --> 00:05:43.522
You can go on there and he has archives of sermons and Bible study notes—all kinds of amazing stuff for you to grow spiritually.

00:05:43.523 --> 00:05:50.568
It's like a family over there. It costs money because the app he uses costs a lot to maintain.

00:05:50.569 --> 00:05:58.959
I think it's like ten bucks a month for the membership, but it's worth it, trust me.

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:11.013
I went over there and I'm growing even more spiritually than I already am. I keep getting nuggets.

00:06:11.014 --> 00:06:17.695
It's a family; you can ask questions and they have a chat where you can talk to other people.

00:06:17.696 --> 00:06:22.981
It's just really cool. I wasn't even going to go there, but I feel like people should know this.

00:06:22.982 --> 00:06:30.622
If we look at what happened in 2017—I've told you all this—I look at what happened with Israel.

00:06:30.623 --> 00:06:41.719
I believe it was a sign for Israel in 2017. Why wouldn't it be a sign for Israel in 2023?

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:58.645
When we look at what happened in September of 2017, a couple of months later Donald Trump went to Israel, and then in May, Jerusalem became the capital of Israel because we moved our embassy there.

00:06:58.646 --> 00:07:16.325
There was so much that happened within that nine-month birthing cycle from September to May. Look at all that happened.

00:07:16.326 --> 00:07:24.414
I believe once we see this next week, when we have this sign in the sky again, let's just watch and see if something happens with Israel.

00:07:24.415 --> 00:07:32.448
If it doesn't and people think it has to do with the Rapture, then great. I hope Jesus comes back this year or next year.

00:07:32.449 --> 00:07:38.573
I'm looking for him to come back today, but let's just watch and see if it has to do with Israel.

00:07:38.574 --> 00:07:46.288
I know they said they were delaying the peace agreement with Syria right now; I saw it on the news.

00:07:46.289 --> 00:07:55.391
They were trying to do the two-state solution, and Syria was irritated about some things.

00:07:55.392 --> 00:08:06.190
I was asking the Lord because he's been speaking to me about authority and teaching you all your authority for what's coming, because it's very serious.

00:08:06.191 --> 00:08:23.035
I told you about the suppression and that everything I've warned you all about is kicking off. We're going to start to see the acceleration.

00:08:23.036 --> 00:08:36.072
For Rosh Hashanah, when we went into last Saturday and the holiday, the atmosphere was charged.

00:08:36.073 --> 00:08:47.484
It was almost like you were able to step over spiritually. It hasn't gone away; you can feel the intensity when you're praying and interceding.

00:08:47.485 --> 00:09:15.606
I want to go back to the authority of the believer. I was telling you all about the visitation I had from the devil.

00:09:15.607 --> 00:09:24.894
I was asleep and I woke up in the middle of the night, and he was standing at the foot of my bed.

00:09:24.895 --> 00:09:33.581
The whole room was lit up like a light bulb, glowing with a dingy white light.

00:09:33.582 --> 00:09:47.302
His hair was flowing, and his clothes were beautiful. Everything about him, other than his eyes, looked like an angel of light.

00:09:47.303 --> 00:09:59.197
But his eyes were so black, like onyx. It was the most intense evil I've ever experienced.

00:09:59.198 --> 00:10:11.429
I froze in my bed. I hate talking about this, but I feel it's necessary to teach you.

00:10:11.430 --> 00:10:21.594
I froze in that fear because I was intimidated at the time by his presence.

00:10:21.595 --> 00:10:31.785
He offered to show me the vastness of what he had authority over, specifically the financial sector.

00:10:31.786 --> 00:10:54.493
He told me, 'If you bow your knee to me and serve me, I will give you all of this.'He showed me pictures of things I'd ever wanted, like Ferraris—lust of the flesh.

00:10:54.494 --> 00:11:01.405
How I was able to see this stuff in a vision, I have no idea. This is all weird for me.

00:11:01.406 --> 00:11:08.433
He was trying to show off everything he had, but he has nothing; he's evil.

00:11:08.434 --> 00:11:15.058
I'm not giving glory to the devil, so I'm going to step out of this now.

00:11:15.059 --> 00:11:21.578
After all that happened, I was sitting in my bed praying in the spirit, and I started praying in tongues.

00:11:21.579 --> 00:11:36.574
He started laughing at me because I told him, 'Get out of my house in the name of Jesus!'But he kept laughing because I was in fear.

00:11:36.575 --> 00:11:48.514
The devil knows when you know who you are. He knows when you have that spark and authority to cast him out.

00:11:48.515 --> 00:11:54.837
You can say 'in the name of Jesus'with your mouth, but if you're trembling in fear, he knows.

00:11:54.838 --> 00:12:09.240
I heard the Holy Spirit speak up inside of me, saying, 'Pray in tongues right now.'I started praying, and he was laughing at the foot of my bed.

00:12:09.241 --> 00:12:30.990
Mind you, the whole room is glowing with demonic light. I was interceding, and all of a sudden the Holy Spirit came over me like fire.

00:12:30.991 --> 00:12:42.552
That authority I'm talking about rose up out of my belly and roared out of me as I started praying in tongues, stirring myself up in my Most Holy Faith.

00:12:42.553 --> 00:12:49.947
'Perfect love casts out all fear.''Greater is he that is in me.'I was quoting those scriptures inside my heart as he was laughing.

00:12:49.947 --> 00:13:10.667
It was like the guy laughing at the end of Michael Jackson's 'Thriller'—a demonic laughter.

00:13:10.668 --> 00:13:27.600
At that moment, I kept praying in the spirit and said, 'In the name of Jesus, I command you to get out of my house now!'I got angry, and the lights all turned off.

00:13:27.601 --> 00:13:52.889
Everything went pitch black again. When the power of God came over me and I got bold as a lion, Satan himself could not stand in the presence of the Almighty God inside of me.

00:13:52.890 --> 00:14:13.182
Greater is he that is in you than he that is in the world. It's like a police officer in uniform holding a stop sign.

00:14:13.183 --> 00:14:33.198
He has authority given to him by the government. People stop not because of the person, but because of the uniform, the badge, and the authority behind them.

00:14:33.199 --> 00:15:29.039
They are operating by the laws of the land. He holds up that sign and everybody stops because they recognize the authority.

00:15:29.040 --> 00:15:43.999
If you don't stop and you hit them, you're going to jail. You automatically know that person is walking in authority.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:16:11.412
But if anyone else is out there without a badge or uniform, you're going to tell them to get out of the way.

00:16:11.413 --> 00:16:17.495
That's how the enemy is. He recognizes when you know your authority.

00:16:17.496 --> 00:16:39.115
He knows by the uniform you have on—that Holy Ghost power on the inside of you.

00:16:39.116 --> 00:16:50.436
A fly will not land on a hot stove. When you are on fire for the Lord, the enemy recognizes it.

00:16:50.437 --> 00:17:31.072
He didn't recognize my authority at first because I was in fear, but when that power came up out of my belly—rivers of living water—the Word came out of me with dunamis behind it.

00:17:31.073 --> 00:17:58.419
I told him to get out, and boom, the lights went out. The devil understands authority.

00:17:58.420 --> 00:18:02.759
Smith Wigglesworth used to tell a story about a lady at a bus stop.

00:18:02.760 --> 00:18:07.099
Her little dog was rubbing up against her legs, wanting to go with her.

00:18:07.100 --> 00:18:12.059
She said, 'Honey, I told you to get back to the house,'but the dog kept following.

00:18:12.060 --> 00:18:19.499
Finally, she shouted, 'I told you to get!'and that dog bolted back to the house. That's how you have to talk to the devil.

00:18:19.500 --> 00:18:19.599
The Bible says in James to submit yourself to God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:18:19.600 --> 00:19:49.479
You have to know your authority. Get inside the scripture so you realize who you are. Ephesians chapter 2 says God is rich in mercy.

00:19:49.480 --> 00:20:12.286
Even when we were dead in sins, he quickened us together with Christ and raised us up to sit together in heavenly places.

00:20:12.287 --> 00:20:57.649
We are seated with him. He raised us up to show the exceeding riches of his grace.

00:20:57.650 --> 00:21:33.374
We are his workmanship, created for good works. We are seated with him in heavenly places.

00:21:33.375 --> 00:22:09.432
Acts 19:15 says the evil spirit answered, 'Jesus I know, and Paul I know, but who are you?'The devil knew those men didn't know who they were.

00:22:09.433 --> 00:22:23.226
I wasn't operating in authority at first because of fear, but I had to switch over to faith.

00:22:23.227 --> 00:22:31.627
'Perfect love casteth out all fear.'He that fears is not made perfect in love. I had to realize my Father loves me.

00:22:31.628 --> 00:23:16.521
The seven sons of Sceva were saying, 'We adjure you by the Jesus whom Paul preaches.'They didn't have a revelation of who Jesus was; they were just using Paul's words.

00:23:16.522 --> 00:24:30.207
Because they didn't have that revelation, the devil beat them up.

00:24:30.208 --> 00:25:29.584
Philippians 2:9 says God has highly exalted him and given him a name above every name, that at the name of Jesus every knee should bow—in heaven, on earth, and under the earth.

00:25:29.585 --> 00:26:04.140
That name gives us power. 1 John 5:18 says whosoever is born of God does not sin, but he that is begotten of God keeps himself and the wicked one touches him not.

00:26:04.141 --> 00:26:23.290
Memorize that. The wicked one cannot touch you because you are begotten of God.

00:26:23.291 --> 00:26:58.952
We have authority to call those things that be not as though they are.

00:26:58.953 --> 00:27:20.035
Jesus is the head, and we are the body. The body and the head are dependent on each other.

00:27:20.036 --> 00:27:40.959
We are his mouth in this earth. We operate in authority over demonic spirits. We are joint-heirs with Jesus Christ.

00:27:40.960 --> 00:27:54.717
We have authority to tread on serpents and scorpions—meaning demonic spirits—and nothing shall by any means harm you.

00:27:54.718 --> 00:28:20.418
We even have authority over the weather. You can speak to the weather just like Jesus said, 'Peace, be still.'The same power dwells in you.

00:28:20.419 --> 00:28:33.726
I practice this daily. Once, a massive tornado was coming toward our house.

00:28:33.727 --> 00:29:06.663
My family ran into the storm cellar, but I stayed in the carport.

00:29:06.664 --> 00:29:14.160
I pointed my finger and said, 'In the name of Jesus Christ, I command you to go up into those clouds!

00:29:14.161 --> 00:29:22.327
You do not come down and touch our house!'I used my authority.

00:29:22.328 --> 00:29:31.663
I could see the clouds turning, trying to come back down, but they went back up.

00:29:31.664 --> 00:29:46.759
You have the power to speak to storms and make mountains move.

00:29:46.760 --> 00:30:06.836
People often ask me to pray for them, and I have compassion, but if you realize the Holy Ghost lives inside you, you can speak to sickness and disease yourself.

00:30:06.837 --> 00:30:40.786
I call in high-pressure and low-pressure systems. I call in cold fronts from Canada to bring cooler temperatures.

00:30:40.787 --> 00:31:18.952
I speak to the jet streams. Jesus spoke to the storms, and you can speak to the storms in your life—fires, hurricanes, or tornadoes.

00:31:18.953 --> 00:31:35.621
It takes faith. Sometimes I call for rain and it takes a few days to get here, but I don't lose faith.

00:31:35.622 --> 00:31:58.389
Other times, it happens immediately. Once, I was in deep intercession and it started raining on my car with not a cloud in the sky.

00:31:58.390 --> 00:32:05.425
It was a sign of the glorious outpouring and revival coming.

00:32:05.426 --> 00:32:45.673
Speak over your finances, your health, and your children. Listen to that still, small voice.

00:32:45.674 --> 00:33:04.950
I saw news articles about people setting up tents for a new virus—some kind of Ebola thing in England.

00:33:04.951 --> 00:33:10.900
It looked like what the Lord showed me in the supernatural. These things are starting to manifest.

00:33:10.901 --> 00:33:51.388
You need the power and authority of the name of Jesus so that when you pray over empty pots, the food multiplies.

00:33:51.389 --> 00:34:00.797
God is the multiplier. He is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all we ask or think, according to the power that works in us.

00:34:00.798 --> 00:34:55.360
Walk in that 'holy glow'like liquid honey. Meditate on Psalms 91 and Psalms 23 until you know who you are in Christ.

00:34:55.361 --> 00:35:40.799
When the enemy tries to deliver a 'package'of sickness, say, 'No, devil, I don't receive that in Jesus'name.'The devil is a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour, but you don't have to let him devour you.

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:50.482
2 Timothy 1:7 says God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:35:50.483 --> 00:36:00.931
I don't have Alzheimer's or dementia; I have the mind of Christ.

00:36:00.932 --> 00:37:04.345
I walk in great peace and joy. You shall know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:37:04.346 --> 00:37:42.650
Faith comes by hearing and hearing the Word of God. You need to hear it until it becomes rhema and revelation knowledge.

00:37:42.651 --> 00:38:05.601
Abraham became fully persuaded that what God had promised, he was able to perform.

00:38:05.602 --> 00:38:19.395
He didn't focus on the deadness of Sarah's womb; he was strong in faith, giving glory to God.

00:38:19.396 --> 00:40:13.041
He didn't stagger at the promise. I hope this sermon helped you.

00:40:13.042 --> 00:40:55.315
I'm going to pray for you. Father, I thank you for my subscribers. I thank you that everything they touch prospers.

00:40:55.316 --> 00:41:30.597
I believe for a hundredfold return and a quick manifestation of finances for them.

00:41:30.598 --> 00:41:39.081
I call them healed, delivered, and free from demonic oppression.

00:41:39.082 --> 00:42:23.833
By the stripes of Jesus, they are whole. Every debt is obliterated.

00:42:23.834 --> 00:42:50.272
They are mentally, physically, and emotionally free by the blood of the Lamb.

00:42:50.273 --> 00:43:18.160
For whom the Son sets free is free indeed. Have a blessed day, y'all. We'll see you next time. Bye-bye.

